These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, january, june, may, august
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, car, bus, snowmobile, motorbike
House: tower, modern, palace, colonial, cottage
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, begonia, rose, daisy
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the cottage house##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the modern house is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person driving the car is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the tower house is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the modern house is the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the palace house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Birthday         | january  | march    | may | june    | august  |
| Transport   | car  | scooter | bus | snowmobile | motorbike  |
| House           | tower     | cottage     | colonial  | modern   | palace    |
| Flower         | begonia | rose    | amaryllis | bellflower  | daisy |

