.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, purple, apricot, yellow, brown
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, blend, siglo, davidoff
5 different games are played: go, domino, poker, chess, whist
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, sunflower, balloon-flower, rose
 1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is the person playing domino##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person who likes apricot is the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who likes apricot##1
10. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the person who likes apricot is the montecristo-smoker##1
13. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Color          | apricot        | brown | purple     | yellow      | grey  |
| Cigar           | montecristo   | blend | davidoff    | siglo | havana |
| Game   | poker | chess     | whist | go    | domino  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | orchid | dahlia    | rose      | sunflower    |

