.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
City: hamburg, prague, colone, rome, edinburgh
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, cricket, skiing, skateboarding, cycling
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, july, october, september, january
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, scientist, dancer, designer, fisherman
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the right of the scientist##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the fisherman is in the middle##1
10. the dancer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| City      | rome          | colone  | prague       | hamburg     | edinburgh      |
| Sport         | cricket | cycling | skateboarding  | skiing   | volleyball    |
| Birthday   | july        | january | march | september    | october   |
| Job     | dressmaker   | dancer | fisherman      | scientist | designer |

