5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, alhambra, blend, bluemaster, bolivar
The people have 5 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer, paramedic, project-manager, musician
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the alhambra-smoker is the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the prince-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
 5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the paramedic is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 7. the software-developer is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the musician is in the middle##1
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is the blend-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the librarian is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday          | july        | december       | october | january   | february  |
| Color   | purple | azure | mauve | coral   | yellow |
