The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel, epic, satire, fantasy
House: townhouse, colonial, farmhouse, ranch-style, tower
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, ship, van, tram, roller
 1. the colonial house is the person driving the van##1
 2. the person driving the van is the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the colonial house##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the tower house is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the colonial house##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| City          | miami    | nizza  | berlin | hannover    | liverpool      |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy | epic | disaster  | satire | time-travel |
| House   | farmhouse           | colonial      | tower      | ranch-style        | townhouse     |
| Transport         | ship         | van  | airplane   | tram       | roller  |

