There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, water, tea, cola
City: prague, colone, miami, liverpool, paris
 1. the person driving the car is the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
12. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Birthday         | april  | october  | november    | january | august |
| Transport   | car        | bike  | taxi | ship      | trike        |
