 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the rat##1
 3. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the modern house is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the art-deco house##1
11. the owner of the mouse is the wooden house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is the alhambra-smoker##1
13. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
