.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, d&b, rock, trance, punk
There 5 different types of food: pepper, radish, lettuce, corn, onion
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, orange, aquamarine, light-blue, white
5 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, rabbit, bird, mouse
 1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person eating radish##1
 4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes white is the person eating onion##1
12. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
13. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |       3       |       4       |      5      |
| Music-Genre    | punk    | rock     | trance | house           | d&b |
| Food         | pepper | corn   | radish      | onion | lettuce     |
| Color       | orange  | light-blue | aquamarine      | white    | lilac    |
| Pet   | bird    | mouse      | rabbit    | hamster           | dog    |

