.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
House: wooden, palace, cape-cod, gothic-revival, colonial
There are 5 different nationalities: polish, colombian, mexican, japanese, italian
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, quad-bike, bike, motorbike
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, september, july, april, march
 1. the colombian is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the wooden house is on the far left##1
 3. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the polish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the polish##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the colonial house is on the right of the palace house##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the italian##1
12. the mexican is the person driving the bike##1
13. the italian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| House      | wooden      | palace       | colonial         | gothic-revival  | cape-cod |
| Nationality   | mexican  | japanese | colombian | polish  | italian  |
| Transport   | bike    | helicopter    | bus        | motorbike | quad-bike     |
| Birthday           | september | july      | august       | april   | march   |

