.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, puzzles, collecting, chess
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, scooter, bike, boat
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, oliveros, pall-mall, swisher, havana
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, australian, indonesian, canadian, polish
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the polish##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the australian is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the indian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is the person driving the boat##1
11. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
