.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, singing, dancing, daffodiling
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, yellow, apricot, red, amber
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil, zinnia, sunflower, rose
The people have 5 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist, chef, engineer, coach
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the scientist##1
 3. the person who likes amber is the paramedic##1
 4. the chef is on the far right##1
 5. the scientist is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the coach is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 8. the coach is on the left of the paramedic##1
 9. the paramedic is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left of the coach##1
12. the person who likes apricot is the person who's hobby is daffodiling##1
13. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
