.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, aconite, tulip, daffodil
5 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, goldfish, ferret, bird
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, weightlifting, water-polo, climbing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, january, october, september, april
 1. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
13. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who growstulip##1
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Flower      | marigold | tulip   | aconite    | begonia       | daffodil |
| Pet   | goldfish           | goat   | bird   | ferret       | hamster  |
| Sport   | snowboarding       | rowing | weightlifting | water-polo     | climbing   |
| Birthday     | october    | january   | september   | february | april   |

 